  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-main">
          <h2>What is SIP (Systematic Investment Plan)?</h2>
          <p>SIP is a method of investing a fixed amount regularly (usually monthly) into mutual funds. Instead of investing a lump sum, SIP lets you build wealth gradually by investing small amounts consistently. The magic of SIP lies in two principles: rupee cost averaging (you buy more units when markets are low and fewer when high) and the power of compounding (your returns generate further returns over time).</p>
          <p>Even a modest SIP of ₹5,000 per month at 12% returns can grow to over ₹50 lakhs in 20 years — where your total investment is only ₹12 lakhs. That's more than 4x growth through compounding alone.</p>

          <h3>How is SIP Return Calculated?</h3>
          <p>SIP returns use the future value of annuity formula: FV = P × [((1+r)^n – 1) / r] × (1+r), where P is the monthly SIP amount, r is the expected monthly rate of return (annual rate / 12 / 100), and n is the total number of months. This accounts for each monthly instalment growing at compound interest for its remaining investment duration.</p>

          <div class="calculator-widget">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-line" style="color: var(--primary); margin-right: 8px;"></i> SIP Calculator</h3>
            <div class="calc-form-group">
              <label for="sipAmount">Monthly SIP Amount: <strong id="sipDisplay">₹10,000</strong></label>
              <input type="range" id="sipAmount" min="500" max="200000" value="10000" step="500">
              <div class="calc-range-labels"><span>₹500</span><span>₹2,00,000</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-form-group">
              <label for="expectedReturn">Expected Return (% p.a.): <strong id="returnDisplay">12%</strong></label>
              <input type="range" id="expectedReturn" min="6" max="20" value="12" step="0.5">
              <div class="calc-range-labels"><span>6%</span><span>20%</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-form-group">
              <label for="sipTenure">Investment Period (Years): <strong id="tenureDisplay">10 Years</strong></label>
              <input type="range" id="sipTenure" min="1" max="30" value="10" step="1">
              <div class="calc-range-labels"><span>1 Year</span><span>30 Years</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="calc-result">
              <div class="calc-result-item"><span class="calc-label">Total Wealth Created</span><span class="calc-value" id="totalWealth">₹23,23,391</span></div>
              <div class="calc-result-item"><span class="calc-label">Amount Invested</span><span class="calc-value" id="totalInvested">₹12,00,000</span></div>
              <div class="calc-result-item"><span class="calc-label">Wealth Gained</span><span class="calc-value" id="wealthGained">₹11,23,391</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>SIP Growth Over Time</h3>
          <table class="rate-table">
            <thead><tr><th>Monthly SIP</th><th>Period</th><th>Invested</th><th>@12% Returns</th><th>Wealth Gain</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>₹5,000</td><td>5 Years</td><td>₹3,00,000</td><td>₹4,12,432</td><td>₹1,12,432</td></tr>
              <tr><td>₹5,000</td><td>10 Years</td><td>₹6,00,000</td><td>₹11,61,695</td><td>₹5,61,695</td></tr>
              <tr><td>₹10,000</td><td>15 Years</td><td>₹18,00,000</td><td>₹50,45,760</td><td>₹32,45,760</td></tr>
              <tr><td>₹10,000</td><td>20 Years</td><td>₹24,00,000</td><td>₹99,91,479</td><td>₹75,91,479</td></tr>
              <tr><td>₹25,000</td><td>25 Years</td><td>₹75,00,000</td><td>₹4,69,83,952</td><td>₹3,94,83,952</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <h3>Why Use Our SIP Calculator?</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> <strong>Visualize Compounding</strong> — See how small monthly investments snowball into crores over decades</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> <strong>Goal-Based Planning</strong> — Calculate the SIP needed for child education, retirement, or home purchase</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> <strong>Return Scenarios</strong> — Compare conservative (8%), moderate (12%), and aggressive (15%) return scenarios</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> <strong>Rupee Cost Averaging</strong> — Understand how SIP reduces the impact of market volatility</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> <strong>Step-Up SIP</strong> — Plan annual SIP increases aligned with salary growth for accelerated wealth</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> <strong>Free & Instant</strong> — No sign-up required, calculate unlimited times</li>
