          <h3>How to Use This Calculator</h3>
          <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">1</div><h4>Set SIP Amount</h4><p>Enter the amount you can invest monthly — start as low as ₹500 and increase over time.</p></div>
            <div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">2</div><h4>Expected Return Rate</h4><p>Use 12% for equity funds, 8-10% for hybrid, and 6-7% for debt funds as a guideline.</p></div>
            <div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">3</div><h4>Choose Duration</h4><p>Longer duration = dramatically higher returns due to compounding. Aim for 10+ years.</p></div>
            <div class="step-card"><div class="step-num">4</div><h4>See Your Wealth</h4><p>View total corpus, amount invested, and wealth gained. Start your SIP today!</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>

